  <li id="comment-5795" class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Anonymous</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2007/05/a-better-day/#comment-5795"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2007-06-01T22:05:00-04:00">Friday, June 1, 2007 at 10:05 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Carless is Seattle is not so bad. Sprawl in this part of country is nothing compared to anywhere in the Midwest. We&#8217;ve adjusted to packing more travel-friendly items to bring to gatherings. Unfortunately, my shoe collection has become much more utilitarian; but being carless has relieved much unnecessary stress in our lives. Carrying our cat to the vet in the rain in a carboard carrier has been a challenge. Yes, the rain sucks, but so does traffic.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
